<main id="main">
    @* <section> *@
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <h1 class="text-center pt-5 ">
            Leave Request Management App
        </h1><hr />
        <div style="border:3px solid Black" class=" mt-4"><img src="~/images/portfolio/leave request management app/app.png" alt="Leave Request Management App" title="Leave Request Management App" loading="lazy" class="img-fluid w-100 d-block img-thumbnail" /></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid mt-3">
        <div class="row mt-5 mx-2">
            <div class="col-lg-9 p-3 mt-4 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center" style="background-color:aliceblue">
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 mb-4 bg-white">
                    <h4 class="mt-4 m-3">Overview</h4>
                    <p class="m-3">The Leave Request Management App, developed using Power Apps Canvas App, is a comprehensive digital solution designed to streamline the leave management process within organizations. The application serves as a centralized platform where employees can effortlessly submit leave requests, monitor their approval status, and track their remaining leave balance, while HR or managers can efficiently manage and approve leave applications in real time. The solution aims to reduce manual intervention, paperwork, and confusion, while promoting clarity and self-service accessibility for all employees.</p>
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Key Features:</h5>
                    <ul class="m-3">
                        <li><span class="fw-semibold">Dashboard Overview:</span> Summary of total, pending, approved, and rejected requests.</li>
                        <li><span class="fw-semibold">Leave Balance Tracking:</span> Visual display of Annual, Sick, and Casual leave balances.</li>
                        <li><span class="fw-semibold">Recent Activity Log:</span> Instant status updates on recently submitted leave requests.</li>
                        <li><span class="fw-semibold">Request & Approval Workflow:</span>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Employees can submit leave requests.</li>
                                <li>HR/Admins can review and approve/reject from a dedicated interface.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <img src="~/images/portfolio/leave request management app/app.png" alt="App" title="App" loading="lazy" class="img-fluid w-100 d-block img-thumbnail" />
                    <hr />
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Impact:</h5>
                    <p class="m-3">The implementation of the Leave Request App brought significant improvements to the internal operations. It eliminated the need for manual tracking of employee leave through spreadsheets and emails, replacing it with a centralized, real-time system accessible to both employees and managers. The app streamlined the entire leave lifecycle—from request to approval—resulting in faster turnaround times and reduced administrative workload for HR teams. Employees gained transparency and control over their leave balances and request statuses, leading to improved satisfaction and fewer follow-ups.</p>
                    <hr />
                    <h5 class="m-3">Explore More:</h5>
                    <p class="m-3">
                        This is just one of the many solutions we’ve developed on the Microsoft Power Platform.
                        If you're looking to digitize operations, improve data control, and simplify complex workflows — we can help.
                    </p>
                    <p class="m-3"> <a asp-controller="Portfolio" asp-action="Index" class="text-decoration-none">Explore Our Full Portfolio</a></p>
                    <hr />
                    <div>
                        <h5>Contact Information:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@voxtus.com" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">info@voxtus.com</a></li>
                            <li>Phone:+91-8630235507</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3">
                <div class="mt-4 p-3" style="background-color:ghostwhite">
                    <h4 class="mt-3">Project information</h4><hr />
                    <h6 class="mt-3">Category: App Design</h6>
                    <h6 class="mt-3">Client: Accountable Value Financial Services</h6>
                    <h6 class="mt-3">Project date: 22 July, 2025</h6>
                    <h6 class="mt-3">
                        Information Technology:
                    </h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Canvas App</li>
                        <li>Microsoft Dataverse</li>
                    </ul>
